01:02:53,083 --> 01:02:59,583
"With my tears I have
washed away my pain."

647
01:02:59,666 --> 01:03:06,750
"The one for whom
I waited for ages crying"

648
01:03:06,833 --> 01:03:14,833
"When I found my beloved
she belonged to someone else."

